objects.query: Select Id,Name, FinServ__Active__c, FinServ__FromField__c, FinServ__FromObject__c, FinServ__FromRecordType__c, FinServ__LookupField__c, FinServ__Namespace__c, FinServ__RollupOperation__c, FinServ__ToField__c, FinServ__ToObject__c, FinServ__UpdateOnChange__c, FinServ__WhereClause__c,External_Id__c from FinServ__RollupByLookupConfig__c where FinServ__Active__c =true

select Id,FinServ__FieldName__c, FinServ__FieldValue__c, FinServ__Operator__c, FinServ__RollupByLookupConfig__c,Name,External_Id__c from FinServ__RollupByLookupFilterCriteria__c where External_Id__c != null

SELECT Id, Name, FinServ__EnableAARInverseRoleUpdate__c, FinServ__EnableBusinessReferralsMade__c, FinServ__EnableGroupRecordRollups__c, FinServ__EnableRollupSummary__c, FinServ__GroupRecordRollupTimestamp__c, FinServ__InteractionUpdateFrequency__c, FinServ__ReferrerScoreCalcEnabled__c, FinServ__RejectedReferralStatus__c, FinServ__RollupSummaryTimestamp__c FROM FinServ__WealthAppConfig__c
SELECT Id, Name, FinServ__Enable__c FROM FinServ__UsePersonAccount__c
